message.content: The registry key "Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon" contains values related to user logon settings. Notably, the "Userinit" value includes an additional executable "C:\WINDOWS\system32\sdra64.exe" alongside the legitimate "C:\WINDOWS\system32\userinit.exe". This suggests a potential malicious payload as legitimate processes are often targeted for exploitation. Further analysis of "sdra64.exe" is recommended to determine its nature and potential impact on the system.
